# Copy to config/open-core-markers.txt (gitignored) and add YOUR internal markers
# (regex, one per line). The open-core guard (scripts/check-open-core.sh, run in CI)
# fails if any appears in a tracked file — a safety net against leaking private
# codenames, account IDs, or vault paths. Lines starting with # are ignored.
#
# YOUR_ACCOUNT_LOCATOR
# your-internal-codename
# op://YourVault
